org.semanticweb.owl.simpleowlapi

  • Classes in org.semanticweb.owl.simpleowlapi used by org.semanticweb.owl.simpleowlapi 
    Class and Description
    Parser
    Represents a Parser wrapper class for working with the Manchester OWL syntax.
    Provider
    Represents a Provider class providing a default implementation for getting a short form, human-readable label for an entity with an IRI from an ontology.
    SelectedReasoner
    Represents a SelectedReasoner class that catalogues / enumerates metadata about OWL 2 reasoners which simpleOWLAPI is able to interact with.
    SimpleOWLAPIFactory
    Core class for simpleOWLAPI which provides access to all methods for constructing and editing OWL ontologies.
    SimpleOWLReasoner
    Class for simpleOWLAPI which provides access to methods for reasoning with OWL ontologies.
